<% if @is_overdue %>
PAYMENT REMINDER - INVOICE OVERDUE
===================================
<% else %>
PAYMENT REMINDER - DUE SOON
===========================
<% end %>

Dear <%= @client.name %>,

<% if @is_overdue %>
Invoice <%= @invoice.invoice_number %> is <%= @days_overdue %> days past due.

This is a friendly reminder that your payment of <%= number_to_currency(@invoice.total_amount) %> was due on <%= @invoice.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>.
<% else %>
Invoice <%= @invoice.invoice_number %> is due in <%= @days_until_due %> days.

This is a friendly reminder that your payment of <%= number_to_currency(@invoice.total_amount) %> is due on <%= @invoice.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>.
<% end %>

INVOICE DETAILS
---------------
Invoice Number: <%= @invoice.invoice_number %>
Issue Date: <%= @invoice.issue_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
Due Date: <%= @invoice.due_date.strftime('%B %d, %Y') %>
Total Amount: <%= number_to_currency(@invoice.total_amount) %>

From: <%= @account.name %>

---

If you have already made this payment, please disregard this reminder. If you have any questions about this invoice, please don't hesitate to contact us.

Thank you for your business!
